              <li>The clear indication shall be made in as concrete and detailed a manner possible, including with regard to the work environment.</li>
              <li>In cases where it is possible that the Content of Duties to be Performed etc., as clearly indicated, will differ from the Content of Duties to be Performed etc. at the time of execution of the work agreement, this fact shall be clearly indicated alongside the Content of Duties to be Performed etc., and in cases where the Content of Duties to be Performed etc. will be different from the content that has already been clearly indicated, the candidate shall be informed promptly.</li>
